metadata.name: kissed Lu Ming
metadata.description:
like lightning, blushing, and raised her glass and said, "Brother Ming, Yao Er will reward you."



Lu Ming took the glass and said, "Yao Er, you invite me to drink a cup of orchid wine with blood tongue every day. I really appreciate having you by my side."



Then he took up his cup and drank it down.



The aroma of wine on the tip of the tongue, Lu Ming's heart is as sweet as the aroma of wine, but the next moment, he feels some spinning.
